title: Hour 1 - Aaron Judge Hits #60, Urban Meyer Speculation
itunes:title: Hour 1 - Aaron Judge Hits #60, Urban Meyer Speculation
description:
Dan thinks it would be a huge risk to sign Aaron Judge to a 10-year deal despite his Triple Crown season. And he speculates about the future of Urban Meyer and when we might see him back on a college football sideline.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
